 2005-05412005-04-07HERITAGE,  ,  ,  , 
ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of HELEN RAY del VAL of North Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years; designate HELEN RAY del VAL for the Pacific region, as established under subsection 10(1.1) of that Act; and determine that HELEN RAY del VAL shall reside within 100 kilometres of the Pacific regional office; effective May 30, 2005.
